items.name: Spreads Once Again Organic Crunchy Almond Butter
items.display_name: Once Again Organic Crunchy Almond Butter
items.details: One Ingredient: organic almonds! Gluten free. Vegan. Kosher certified. Sodium free. Unsweetened - no sugar. USDA organic. Non GMO project verified. nongmoproject.org. Employee-owned. Founded in 1976. We spread integrity. One Delicious Ingredient: almonds! We have been making almond butter for decades. Our employee owners carefully select only the finest organic almonds available, which are dry roasted and milled with nothing else added. We package in glass jars to preserve the flavor profile and maximize the shelf-life of our products, and glass is conducive to recycling. Our Raccoon Logo: Four baby raccoons grew up on the factory grounds. Apparently orphaned, they really enjoyed our nut butters. So - in turn, we adopted them and created our company logo in their honor. The Once Again Family helped the raccoons in their early months, and then released them into the forest. To this day, our by-products are donated to area farms or to nature lovers who often use them as animal and bird foods. Our mascot, Rocky, has become a symbol of our wholesome nature, our closeness and responsibility to the earth and the nature of our product. Ed's favorite - maintenance manager. OTCO - Certified organic by Oregon Tilth. www.onceagainnutbutter.com. Please recycle glass jars. Product of USA.
